  "title": "Telemarketer",
  "description": "<p><strong>Company Overview</strong></p><p>Since 1981 , DAN IMPACT PTE LTD has been providing general contracting and renovation services to commercial business spaces </p><p><strong>Job Summary</strong></p><p>You will engage potential clients through telemarketing to secure appointments, coordinate with the team to attend meetings, and introduce the company’s services via email. You will also support team members to ensure smooth operations.</p><p><strong>Responsibilities</strong></p><ul><li>Identify and compile potential client contacts into a comprehensive database to support outreach efforts</li><li>Make daily phone calls to potential clients to secure appointments and generate business opportunities</li><li>Coordinate with team members to attend client appointments promptly and effectively</li><li>Send clear and professional emails to potential clients introducing the company’s services and offerings</li><li>Assist team members with various tasks as needed to support overall team performance</li></ul><p><strong>Required competencies and certifications</strong></p><ul><li>Minimum of two years’ experience in a telemarketing role</li></ul>",
